ygData.subject: Re: Where to find sewing kit molds in GFay?
ygData.msgSnippet: No no, skewers take you to 115.  Pots to 122.  I wouldn t bother with sewing kits; making banded will bring you up the rest of the way. Trenfen of Fennin Ro
ygData.messageBody:
No no, skewers take you to 115. Pots to 122. I wouldn't bother with sewing
kits; making banded will bring you up the rest of the way.

Trenfen of Fennin Ro
